text: The Château de Mutigney is a castle in Mutigney, Jura, Franche-Comté, France. ==History== It was built in the 15th century.French Ministry of Culture: Château de Mutigney ==Architectural significance== It has been listed as an official historical monument by the French Ministry of Culture since 1971. ==References== Category:Châteaux in Jura (department) Category:Monuments historiques of Bourgogne-Franche-Comté
title: Château de Mutigney
